iWe can see that there have already been 128,644 requests	/	tilde.team	70
imade by robots that have landed in the labyrinth, with	/	tilde.team	70
iOpenAI and Anthropic as the main senders. Looking at the	/	tilde.team	70
imetrics, I can see that GPTBot is the least intelligent	/	tilde.team	70
iscrapper, having covered the longest path with a depth of	/	tilde.team	70
i79!	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
iTo get an idea of what this represents, imagine clicking 79	/	tilde.team	70
itimes on a word in a text that redirects to a new text, with	/	tilde.team	70
ithis word concatenated at the end of the URL.	/	tilde.team	70
