i## Conclusion	/	tilde.team	70
i	/	tilde.team	70
iI've managed to prevent LLM scrappers from stealing my	/	tilde.team	70
icontent without my permission by using very little RAM and	/	tilde.team	70
iCPU. Only human visitors are allowed to download pages from	/	tilde.team	70
imy websites. This setup allows me to consume fewer resources	/	tilde.team	70
ito serve my content to IAs.	/	tilde.team	70
